## Show Floating Item

---

Shows a floating item to the player.

---

### Example
```json
{
  "type": "origins:action_when_damage_taken",
  "entity_action": {
    "type": "moborigins:show_floating_item",
    "item_stack": {
      "item": "minecraft:creeper_head"
    }
  },
  "cooldown": 1
}
```
Shows a floating creeper head to the player when they take damage.

